title: Chef dec Indiens (Indian Chief), plate 8 from Caravanne du Sultan a la Mecque (Caravan of a Sultan Going to Mecca)
description: Dark-skinned man with mustache leans against low wall. Both hands at belt, from which hangs long curved sword. He faces frontally, and wears stiff striped turban with fur, feathers, and pearls.
